## Description
The **Data Transformation program&nbsp;**resource&nbsp;allows to use&nbsp;a precompiled Doxee Platform 2 Data Transformation (DT) resource to enable data transformation in a workflow.

> Tip

This resource is useful for example to migrate DT resources from Doxee Platform 2 into Doxee Platform 3. 

## Additional creation parameters
None.

## Resource editor
None.

## Release parameters
![](data:image/png;base64,)

Field

Description

**Target**

Select the program type:

- **Batch production&nbsp;**

- **On-demand production**

**File**

Click&nbsp;**Upload**&nbsp;to select a&nbsp;precompiled Data Transformation program, obtained by exporting a DT resource from Doxee Platform 2.

**Summary**

Brief description of the release
